                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8363" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1285</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1701 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国平安：引金融活水，浇灌一片油茶花烂漫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ping An: Bringing in financial water to water a piece of oil tea blossoms</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭名媛，朱琳琳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国平安保险 (集团)股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融创新；风险管理；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial innovation, Risk Management, Rural revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国平安秉承服务社会、回馈国家的初心，以提升金融服务实体经济质效为聚焦点，以产业振兴为主线，持续深入探索开发高质量的保险、金融产品与服务，全面助力实现乡村振兴，促进共同富裕。中国平安保险、金融下乡项目是继村官、村医、村教“三村工程”之后的助力乡村振兴的新模式再升级，首次落地广东韶关。这一项目以乡村优势产业发展为基础，推动全产业链稳定发展，支持产业链延伸，进一步推动乡村振兴，建设和谐美丽乡村，实现农业稳产增收、农民稳定增收、农村稳定平安。本案例通过梳理中国平安助力韶关油茶产业振兴的“保险+创新”、“金融+碳汇”项目的各环节，引导学员思考该项目的动因和具体内容，对金融机构风险管理及金融创新相关领域的知识有所了解，进而思考其对乡村振兴的影响路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Ping An adheres to the original intention of serving the society and giving back to the country, focuses on improving the quality and efficiency of financial services to the real economy, takes industrial revitalisation as the main line, and continues to explore the development of high-quality insurance and financial products and services, to comprehensively assist in the revitalisation of the countryside, and to promote common prosperity. Ping An Insurance and Finance to the Countryside Project is a new model of rural revitalisation following the &quot;Three Villages Project&quot; of village officials, village doctors and village teachers, and has landed in Shaoguan, Guangdong for the first time. This project is based on the development of advantageous industries in the countryside, promotes the stable development of the whole industrial chain, supports the extension of the industrial chain, further promotes the revitalisation of the countryside, builds a harmonious and beautiful countryside, and achieves stable production and income in agriculture, stable income for farmers, and stability and peace in the countryside. By combing through the various aspects of the &quot;insurance + innovation&quot; and &quot;finance + carbon sink&quot; projects of Ping An of China to help Shaoguan oil tea industry revitalisation, the case guides the participants to think about the motivation and specific content of the project, and gain an understanding of the knowledge of financial institutions in the fields of risk management and financial innovation, and then think about their knowledge of risk management and financial innovation. The participants were guided to think about the motivation and specific contents of the project, to understand the risk management and financial innovation of financial institutions, and to think about its impact on rural revitalisation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融机构与金融市场》、《金融创新》、《风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融机构服务和功能；风险管理；金融创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
